WEBVTT

00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:07.220 --> 00:01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:12.020 --> 00:01:15.140
[Episode 32]

00:01:16.750 --> 00:01:17.650
Come check Lifei out.

00:01:31.520 --> 00:01:32.730
Her meridians are reconnected.

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:41.890
Lifei.

00:01:52.910 --> 00:01:54.780
Why did you give me your cultivation?

00:01:56.550 --> 00:01:58.220
We're already advanced in years.

00:01:58.470 --> 00:01:59.530
The spirit energy

00:02:00.080 --> 00:02:00.940
Is useless to us now.

00:02:06.600 --> 00:02:07.220
Elder Zhu.

00:02:08.520 --> 00:02:09.940
Don't dwell on that.

00:02:11.030 --> 00:02:11.780
Lifei,

00:02:12.080 --> 00:02:12.810
Just go.

00:02:13.870 --> 00:02:14.410
Go?

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:16.020
Where to?

00:02:33.830 --> 00:02:37.180
Has the mountain-sea barrier been broken?

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:44.020
We can't escape this great calamity.

00:02:46.990 --> 00:02:50.810
The Sea Calamity came from the bloodshed of immortal sects.

00:02:51.430 --> 00:02:53.410
This sin is of our own making,

00:02:53.920 --> 00:02:55.970
And we must bear it ourselves.

00:02:57.710 --> 00:02:59.780
Leave this to us.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:01.850
Elder Zhu,

00:03:02.830 --> 00:03:04.690
Do you also know the legend of the Sea Calamity?

00:03:08.200 --> 00:03:10.850
Years ago, to hunt for the Divine Tree,

00:03:11.480 --> 00:03:13.060
I pored over ancient scrolls in the Central Plains.

00:03:13.520 --> 00:03:15.130
One scroll recorded

00:03:15.710 --> 00:03:16.970
That 1,000 years ago,

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:19.500
A woman who could absorb heaven and earth's spirit energy

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:21.460
Was slain by immortals in the East Sea.

00:03:22.670 --> 00:03:25.940
That marked the first arrival of the Sea Calamity.

00:03:26.550 --> 00:03:28.970
The Sea Calamity is divine retribution.

00:03:29.550 --> 00:03:30.810
We cannot abide anything

00:03:30.830 --> 00:03:32.570
Different from us

00:03:32.590 --> 00:03:34.180
And seek only to destroy it.

00:03:38.920 --> 00:03:40.530
Our ignorance

00:03:41.150 --> 00:03:43.810
Brought forth this calamity.

00:03:46.270 --> 00:03:47.620
That woman was the Divine Tree.

00:03:49.640 --> 00:03:51.130
The Divine Tree caused the Sea Calamity

00:03:51.990 --> 00:03:53.500
And shall end it.

00:03:58.590 --> 00:04:01.810
Lifei, you've been reborn as a human.

00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:04.410
You're no different from the rest of us.

00:04:05.240 --> 00:04:06.410
The immortal sects

00:04:07.920 --> 00:04:08.970
Have wronged you.

00:04:19.480 --> 00:04:20.450
All things bear

00:04:21.350 --> 00:04:22.570
Their karmic causes and fruits.

00:04:25.150 --> 00:04:27.100
This fate was never yours to carry.

00:04:27.590 --> 00:04:30.450
We will never let you sacrifice yourself.

00:04:33.560 --> 00:04:34.250
Just go.

00:04:35.150 --> 00:04:35.980
Return to Qingqiu.

00:05:04.320 --> 00:05:04.980
It's Xiuyuan!

00:05:05.960 --> 00:05:06.570
Lei!

00:05:55.960 --> 00:05:56.770
The world teeters on collapse.

00:05:57.030 --> 00:05:58.010
We must lay aside old grudges

00:05:58.030 --> 00:05:58.770
And stand united.

00:05:59.520 --> 00:06:01.660
Whether one person, one realm, one sect, one clan,

00:06:02.350 --> 00:06:04.300
Or human, spirit, demon, or monster,

00:06:04.760 --> 00:06:05.770
All are living beings under heaven.

00:06:07.470 --> 00:06:08.500
We must join hands as one.

00:07:02.350 --> 00:07:02.890
Succeeded.

00:07:04.030 --> 00:07:04.740
The earth fire recedes!

00:07:28.230 --> 00:07:28.770
Lifei.

00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:31.620
Where's Lifei?

00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:33.100
Oh, no.

00:08:33.910 --> 00:08:34.500
We can't stop it.

00:09:09.870 --> 00:09:10.610
This time,

00:09:13.350 --> 00:09:14.850
You must not take it back.

00:09:18.680 --> 00:09:20.300
I've failed my father after all.

00:09:24.830 --> 00:09:26.060
We have no regrets about holding out

00:09:28.280 --> 00:09:29.210
Till the very end.

00:09:35.400 --> 00:09:37.020
In the end, everything was a fleeting dream.

00:09:54.680 --> 00:09:55.810
It's better to stay far away

00:09:58.110 --> 00:09:58.850
As long as you live safely.

00:10:29.920 --> 00:10:32.880
♪When fate calls, I rise as a worthy one♪

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:35.640
♪I'll never back down♪

00:10:36.470 --> 00:10:37.020
Lifei.

00:10:37.020 --> 00:10:39.040
♪I keep my former fearless resolve, never return it♪

00:10:39.040 --> 00:10:39.810
It's Lifei.

00:10:42.710 --> 00:10:43.300
Lifei.

00:10:43.300 --> 00:10:45.660
♪Dusk till dawn, I stay awake♪

00:10:45.780 --> 00:10:47.110
♪Bearing heavy missions, I ride far away♪

00:10:47.110 --> 00:10:47.660
Lifei.

00:10:48.900 --> 00:10:53.580
♪The hidden fire in my heart forges a massive sword♪

00:10:53.740 --> 00:10:57.080
♪With you, we climb bleak cliffs beneath endless gloom♪

00:10:57.080 --> 00:10:57.570
Lifei.

00:10:58.100 --> 00:11:00.580
♪Bow our heads and endure bitter gales♪

00:11:00.700 --> 00:11:06.220
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

00:11:06.520 --> 00:11:10.320
♪Let frost, snow and rain block the long stone steps♪

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:12.640
♪I tread fleeting mist beneath my feet♪

00:11:12.920 --> 00:11:18.440
♪At last I see, life's end lies boundless wild free♪

00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:25.680
♪Don't idle away time. We shall meet atop the peak♪

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:26.260
It's enough.

00:11:26.590 --> 00:11:27.140
I'll take you away.

00:11:34.160 --> 00:11:35.570
This is what I have to do.

00:11:35.800 --> 00:11:37.780
I saw the karmic cycle overseas

00:11:37.800 --> 00:11:39.300
That the death of the Divine Tree causes the Sea Calamity.

00:11:39.320 --> 00:11:40.810
The Sea Calamity destroys the world with spirit energy,

00:11:40.830 --> 00:11:42.420
While the Divine Tree is born to absorb spirit energy.

00:11:42.680 --> 00:11:43.780
The two are intertwined

00:11:44.080 --> 00:11:45.330
Yet opposed.

00:11:45.350 --> 00:11:46.690
I only wish to spend my life

00:11:46.990 --> 00:11:49.020
Shielding Xiaobangchui from this disaster.

00:11:51.510 --> 00:11:52.690
The Sea Calamity began because of me,

00:11:54.960 --> 00:11:56.260
So only I can end it.

00:11:59.110 --> 00:11:59.610
Very well.

00:12:00.800 --> 00:12:01.420
I'm with you.

00:12:04.510 --> 00:12:05.140
Xiuyuan.

00:12:05.160 --> 00:12:05.940
We made a vow

00:12:06.800 --> 00:12:07.540
To live together

00:12:08.350 --> 00:12:10.970
Or perish side by side.

00:12:39.590 --> 00:12:40.090
Lifei!

00:12:59.830 --> 00:13:00.610
Master,

00:13:05.040 --> 00:13:07.140
Xiaobangchui and Little Yecha, whom you protected,

00:13:08.350 --> 00:13:09.940
Can finally guard those

00:13:11.110 --> 00:13:13.210
On the Central Plains you cherished.

00:13:16.320 --> 00:13:16.810
Lifei!

00:14:34.840 --> 00:14:38.520
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

00:14:38.840 --> 00:14:41.340
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

00:14:41.800 --> 00:14:45.120
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:47.560
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

00:14:48.600 --> 00:14:52.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

00:14:52.800 --> 00:14:55.160
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

00:14:55.760 --> 00:14:57.280
♪No calamity can rival♪

00:14:57.680 --> 00:15:00.720
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

00:15:02.800 --> 00:15:06.280
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

00:15:07.040 --> 00:15:09.280
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

00:15:09.720 --> 00:15:12.760
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

00:15:13.400 --> 00:15:15.680
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:15:16.480 --> 00:15:19.960
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:15:20.740 --> 00:15:23.020
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

00:15:23.540 --> 00:15:26.500
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

00:15:27.220 --> 00:15:29.420
♪Reign supreme♪

00:15:30.080 --> 00:15:33.160
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

00:15:57.200 --> 00:16:00.880
