00:17:41.160 --> 00:17:43.360
♪Reign supreme♪

00:17:43.960 --> 00:17:47.490
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

00:17:48.160 --> 00:17:50.530
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

00:17:50.850 --> 00:17:54.050
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds, break through the waves♪

00:17:54.650 --> 00:17:56.930
♪The heart's ocean knows no shore♪

00:17:57.330 --> 00:17:58.920
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

00:17:58.920 --> 00:17:59.420
Lifei.

00:18:01.690 --> 00:18:04.090
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

00:18:04.530 --> 00:18:07.690
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:09.660
Lifei.

00:18:09.660 --> 00:18:10.650
♪And falling petals♪

00:18:11.370 --> 00:18:15.640
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

00:18:15.640 --> 00:18:16.660
The immortal sects are far from perfect,

00:18:17.120 --> 00:18:20.050
Yet the world holds countless warm moments,

00:18:20.360 --> 00:18:21.620
Like clusters of tiny flames,

00:18:21.880 --> 00:18:23.770
Chasing away loneliness and cold, bringing hope.

00:18:24.270 --> 00:18:25.250
Someday,

00:18:25.640 --> 00:18:27.450
This world will become what Master hoped for.

00:18:27.790 --> 00:18:28.530
I firmly believe

00:18:28.840 --> 00:18:30.050
That the day will come.

00:18:30.270 --> 00:18:31.730
This is the aspiration of my cultivation.

00:18:32.030 --> 00:18:33.940
My journey in the mortal world

00:18:34.200 --> 00:18:35.690
Has no regrets or sorrows.

00:18:36.120 --> 00:18:39.580
Generations of brilliant souls

00:18:41.270 --> 00:18:42.580
Roamed everywhere

00:18:43.360 --> 00:18:44.340
To quell the Sea Calamity.

00:18:45.990 --> 00:18:47.820
Now the calamity is finally ended,

00:18:48.310 --> 00:18:49.010
But none

00:18:51.680 --> 00:18:52.580
Of them remain.

00:18:58.440 --> 00:18:59.770
Still, I trust the future

00:19:00.600 --> 00:19:02.210
Will unfold just as they wished.

00:19:44.680 --> 00:19:45.290
Sir,

00:19:46.360 --> 00:19:47.210
A letter from Mr. Mo.

00:19:50.920 --> 00:19:52.290
He said the Sea Calamity has vanished,

00:19:52.750 --> 00:19:54.730
And Xiuyuan has sent demons back to their overseas homelands.

00:19:55.360 --> 00:19:55.940
Besides,

00:19:56.440 --> 00:19:57.820
The seaway from the Central Plains to overseas lands

00:19:58.200 --> 00:19:59.820
Rises again after being lost for thousands of years.

00:20:01.440 --> 00:20:02.660
Perhaps the exchange between the Central Plains

00:20:04.030 --> 00:20:05.820
And the outer realms can be restored.

00:20:16.840 --> 00:20:18.820
Truly, only he and she could bring

00:20:19.960 --> 00:20:24.180
Great changes and vitality to the Central Plains.

00:20:25.470 --> 00:20:25.970
Sir,

00:20:27.160 --> 00:20:28.580
The remnant spirits of Lifei and Xiuyuan

00:20:28.710 --> 00:20:30.250
Were taken away by the Nine-Tailed Fox and Mr. Yan.

00:20:31.470 --> 00:20:32.580
Is there a chance

00:20:33.270 --> 00:20:34.210
That they're still alive?

00:20:39.960 --> 00:20:41.140
Heaven pities all living beings.

00:20:41.710 --> 00:20:44.580
Kind hearts and good deeds shall reap good karma.

00:20:45.310 --> 00:20:46.010
There may be

00:20:48.160 --> 00:20:50.010
A glimmer of hope for them.

00:21:02.360 --> 00:21:03.420
A decade reshaped

00:21:04.070 --> 00:21:06.580
All immortal sects in the Central Plains.

00:21:06.920 --> 00:21:08.420
Immortal Lord, we welcome you back from seclusion!

00:21:08.600 --> 00:21:10.970
Immortal Lord, we welcome you back from seclusion!

00:21:11.640 --> 00:21:12.490
One day,

00:21:12.510 --> 00:21:15.530
A purple star crashed over the Xingzheng Hall.

00:21:15.880 --> 00:21:17.050
It was as large as a bushel

00:21:17.360 --> 00:21:19.940
And foretold the arrival of an immortal.

00:21:23.880 --> 00:21:26.180
Ji Tongzhou styled himself Immortal Lord Xuanhua,

00:21:26.600 --> 00:21:29.010
Turning the Xingzheng Hall into the state guardian sect.

00:21:29.710 --> 00:21:31.290
He fought beside the Yue Emperor

00:21:31.710 --> 00:21:32.860
[Adult Ji Jingwu] and vanquished every state,

00:21:33.440 --> 00:21:35.380
Uniting the whole realm.

00:21:36.880 --> 00:21:39.530
The Wuyue Court under Deng Xiguang

00:21:40.070 --> 00:21:42.420
Withdrew from the mortal realm,

00:21:43.070 --> 00:21:44.820
Allowing the Xingzheng Hall to dominate.

00:21:48.960 --> 00:21:51.180
Ji Tongzhou sought to unify the immortal sects.

00:21:51.470 --> 00:21:54.420
He sent the Xuanhua Decree to the Mountain and Sea Sects.

00:21:54.880 --> 00:21:57.940
[Wanxian Sect] Obey, or face destruction.

00:22:00.270 --> 00:22:01.580
Ji Tongzhou goes too far,

00:22:02.030 --> 00:22:03.660
Ordering our sect to yield to the Xingzheng Hall.

00:22:04.270 --> 00:22:05.100
Over the past year,

00:22:05.750 --> 00:22:06.860
Many sects refused to answer

00:22:06.880 --> 00:22:08.450
The summons of the Xuanhua Decree,

00:22:08.880 --> 00:22:10.900
Only to be attacked and wiped out

00:22:11.270 --> 00:22:12.100
By the Xingzheng Hall.

00:22:14.710 --> 00:22:15.340
I heard

00:22:18.470 --> 00:22:19.620
The Dizang Sect has been destroyed as well.

00:22:22.960 --> 00:22:23.580
Jiao,

00:22:24.310 --> 00:22:25.380
I'm heading to the Xingzheng Hall

00:22:25.840 --> 00:22:26.900
To return the Xuanhua Decree.

00:22:27.510 --> 00:22:28.010
No,

00:22:28.270 --> 00:22:29.050
It's far too dangerous.

00:22:29.470 --> 00:22:31.340
Ji Tongzhou was once our fellow disciple.

00:22:31.840 --> 00:22:32.620
He won't harm me

00:22:32.960 --> 00:22:34.100
For old friendship's sake.

00:22:35.640 --> 00:22:36.290
Besides,

00:22:38.360 --> 00:22:39.340
We've had no word

00:22:39.750 --> 00:22:41.580
From Changyue and Ye since the Sea Calamity.

00:22:42.440 --> 00:22:43.450
I want to ask him about them.

00:22:44.230 --> 00:22:44.770
Fine.

00:22:45.550 --> 00:22:46.290
Stay alert.

00:22:46.750 --> 00:22:47.860
Don't push yourself

00:22:48.030 --> 00:22:48.900
If anything goes wrong.

00:22:59.160 --> 00:23:01.450
Your Highness's painting skills grow finer by the day.

00:24:04.070 --> 00:24:05.490
What's wrong? Unwell?

00:24:06.960 --> 00:24:09.580
Nothing. I think I ate something bad.

00:24:21.030 --> 00:24:21.530
Get rid of it.

00:24:24.030 --> 00:24:24.490
Your Highness,

00:24:25.470 --> 00:24:26.490
This is our child.

00:24:26.960 --> 00:24:27.490
I beg you.

00:24:28.030 --> 00:24:29.420
Spare the child, please.

00:24:34.600 --> 00:24:36.290
This must not happen again.

00:24:38.510 --> 00:24:39.660
Do not cling to foolish hopes.

00:24:40.750 --> 00:24:41.290
Your Highness,

00:24:42.230 --> 00:24:43.530
I can give up everything.

00:24:44.120 --> 00:24:44.820
I'm begging you.

00:24:45.360 --> 00:24:47.050
Spare our child, please.

00:25:25.160 --> 00:25:27.250
Are you dead or alive?

00:25:37.600 --> 00:25:38.050
Young lady.

00:25:40.920 --> 00:25:41.690
Miaoqing.

00:25:43.840 --> 00:25:44.690
He's utterly insane.

00:25:45.550 --> 00:25:46.690
He sees you as Lifei's substitute

00:25:46.710 --> 00:25:48.050
And won't even spare his own child.

00:25:50.640 --> 00:25:51.690
Let's confront him right now.

00:25:51.710 --> 00:25:52.290
No.

00:25:55.470 --> 00:25:56.050
Gelin,

00:25:56.960 --> 00:25:57.690
Let go first.

00:26:02.880 --> 00:26:04.420
I know you mean well.

00:26:05.470 --> 00:26:06.820
Don't worry about me.

00:26:07.790 --> 00:26:10.340
I only want to give birth to this child.

00:26:11.360 --> 00:26:11.940
Nothing else

00:26:12.880 --> 00:26:13.620
Matters.

00:26:22.160 --> 00:26:23.200
[Xuanhua Palace]

00:26:23.200 --> 00:26:24.580
Gelin, Lu Li,

00:26:25.070 --> 00:26:26.340
His Highness expected your arrival,

00:26:26.360 --> 00:26:27.140
And here you are.

00:26:29.400 --> 00:26:30.210
His Highness has stepped out,

00:26:30.400 --> 00:26:31.100
But he will return shortly.

00:26:31.470 --> 00:26:32.860
Please wait for him in his chamber.

00:26:37.640 --> 00:26:38.530
I don't know why

00:26:39.230 --> 00:26:41.340
This chamber reminds me of the academy.

00:26:42.200 --> 00:26:43.340
Looks just like our disciple lodgings, right?

00:26:48.750 --> 00:26:50.380
Tongzhou holds onto old memories.

00:26:56.880 --> 00:26:57.530
What's wrong?

00:27:00.470 --> 00:27:01.420
I can't explain it.

00:27:17.160 --> 00:27:17.860
What's wrong?

00:27:32.440 --> 00:27:33.010
No.

00:27:34.030 --> 00:27:34.690
It can't be true.

00:27:35.750 --> 00:27:36.490
It can't be true!

00:27:37.200 --> 00:27:38.820
Gelin, calm down.

00:27:39.160 --> 00:27:40.050
It's only a blade shoulder.

00:27:41.360 --> 00:27:43.210
The sword is the imperial token of Gaolu.

00:27:44.600 --> 00:27:46.250
Ye would never part with it.

00:27:52.270 --> 00:27:54.290
So it's the imperial token of Gaolu.

00:27:57.680 --> 00:27:59.770
No wonder even karmic fire could not burn it.

00:28:06.270 --> 00:28:07.490
- You killed them. - Gelin.

00:28:12.840 --> 00:28:13.580
Why?

00:28:14.750 --> 00:28:15.620
Tell me, why?

00:28:17.440 --> 00:28:19.050
They tried to stop me from killing Lei Xiuyuan.

00:28:21.270 --> 00:28:22.970
They brought it on themselves.

00:28:25.960 --> 00:28:26.450
Gelin,

00:28:27.360 --> 00:28:28.820
They died a decade ago.

00:28:38.510 --> 00:28:39.860
I treated all of you as friends,

00:28:42.960 --> 00:28:44.940
Yet every one of you

00:28:44.960 --> 00:28:46.340
Took that Demon Lord's side

00:28:47.920 --> 00:28:50.250
And betrayed me one after another.

00:28:53.070 --> 00:28:53.820
All of you

00:28:54.990 --> 00:28:56.180
Deserve to die!

00:28:56.440 --> 00:28:57.820
Ji Tongzhou, you beast!

00:29:02.470 --> 00:29:03.380
I'll kill you!

00:29:15.710 --> 00:29:16.860
Take one more step forward,

00:29:17.360 --> 00:29:19.340
And she'll be consumed by karmic fire instantly.

00:29:25.600 --> 00:29:26.250
Ji Tongzhou,

00:29:27.120 --> 00:29:28.690
You let us find Ye Ye's blade shoulder

00:29:28.960 --> 00:29:29.770
And then grievously wounded Gelin.

00:29:30.640 --> 00:29:31.690
What exactly are you after?

00:29:35.310 --> 00:29:37.180
You're the Jiufeng Clan's leader, huh?

00:29:38.030 --> 00:29:40.420
I've heard you spirits have far-reaching intelligence

00:29:41.030 --> 00:29:43.010
And know every landform of the islands

00:29:43.030 --> 00:29:44.250
Like the back of your hand.

00:29:45.360 --> 00:29:46.100
In six months,

00:29:47.710 --> 00:29:50.050
Bring Jiang Lifei before me.

00:29:53.360 --> 00:29:54.250
If you fail,

00:29:55.360 --> 00:29:57.770
Prepare to collect Gelin's ashes.

00:30:00.990 --> 00:30:01.820
Don't hurt her!

00:30:09.200 --> 00:30:09.940
I agree to your terms.

00:30:28.440 --> 00:30:29.140
Mark my words,

00:30:31.640 --> 00:30:32.730
Only six months.

00:30:55.120 --> 00:30:56.340
A decade ago,

00:30:56.680 --> 00:30:58.970
The Divine Tree and Yecha sacrificed themselves

00:30:59.200 --> 00:31:00.290
To fend off the Sea Calamity.

00:31:00.640 --> 00:31:02.690
They ended the age-old karmic hatred,

00:31:02.710 --> 00:31:03.860
Breaking the curse to be reborn.

00:31:04.400 --> 00:31:05.730
The Divine Tree's spirit meridians were completely shattered,

00:31:06.030 --> 00:31:07.690
And Yecha lost his supreme power.

00:31:07.990 --> 00:31:09.420
Though their cultivation faded drastically,

00:31:09.710 --> 00:31:10.940
They finally gained what they longed for.

00:31:12.070 --> 00:31:13.290
Lifei and the others have all left.

00:31:13.880 --> 00:31:15.290
Why are you still writing this tale?

00:31:16.160 --> 00:31:17.580
The story should have ended.

00:31:18.640 --> 00:31:20.010
Yet now, back in the Central Plains,

00:31:21.550 --> 00:31:23.140
We await a new ending.

00:31:24.550 --> 00:31:25.380
Years ago,

00:31:27.070 --> 00:31:28.490
When Qingcheng roamed overseas with me,

00:31:29.270 --> 00:31:30.900
He was worried about the Central Plains

00:31:32.510 --> 00:31:33.530
And insisted on returning.

00:31:35.360 --> 00:31:36.050
This time,

00:31:37.960 --> 00:31:40.100
There must be a different conclusion.

00:31:40.750 --> 00:31:43.210
But old karmic ties in the world remain.

00:31:43.600 --> 00:31:46.450
Ji Tongzhou holds Baili Gelin hostage,

00:31:46.920 --> 00:31:49.490
Forcing Lu Li of the Jiufeng Clan to bring back the Divine Tree.

00:31:49.880 --> 00:31:51.180
Reluctant to leave her old friend,

00:31:51.790 --> 00:31:54.420
The Divine Tree travels home with Yecha.

00:32:01.790 --> 00:32:03.340
Lifei, don't grieve.

00:32:04.360 --> 00:32:05.380
Once you make a choice,

00:32:07.310 --> 00:32:08.340
You must bear its consequences.

00:32:10.550 --> 00:32:11.140
Xiuyuan.

00:32:11.360 --> 00:32:11.940
Lifei,

00:32:12.920 --> 00:32:13.900
My choice

00:32:14.840 --> 00:32:15.770
Has always been you.

00:33:04.880 --> 00:33:05.420
Stand up.

00:33:05.440 --> 00:33:06.140
Thank you.

00:33:10.160 --> 00:33:10.970
Lifei.

00:33:22.880 --> 00:33:23.820
You're with child.

00:33:24.230 --> 00:33:25.450
Don't do heavy labor.

00:33:25.960 --> 00:33:27.140
Focus on safely giving birth to the baby.

00:33:28.160 --> 00:33:29.050
Lifei,

00:33:29.550 --> 00:33:30.820
Do not blame His Highness.

00:33:31.880 --> 00:33:32.490
He...

00:33:35.880 --> 00:33:37.490
He killed my dearest friends

00:33:39.360 --> 00:33:40.420
And took Gelin captive.

00:33:45.960 --> 00:33:46.690
His Highness

00:33:47.710 --> 00:33:49.180
Had no other choice.

00:33:49.880 --> 00:33:51.100
He never meant to hurt anyone.

00:33:52.120 --> 00:33:54.580
Does that excuse how he treated you?

00:33:57.790 --> 00:33:58.940
He's cold to me

00:33:59.960 --> 00:34:01.010
Only because

00:34:02.470 --> 00:34:03.900
I can never be you.

00:34:05.200 --> 00:34:06.250
You'll never be me.

00:34:06.470 --> 00:34:07.420
You belong to yourself.

00:34:07.710 --> 00:34:08.820
You've sacrificed so much for him.

00:34:09.160 --> 00:34:10.820
He ought to cherish and treat you well,

00:34:11.120 --> 00:34:11.860
Instead of...

00:34:11.880 --> 00:34:12.700
I don't blame him.

00:34:14.510 --> 00:34:15.490
I chose this willingly.

00:34:18.070 --> 00:34:19.610
I have no spirit energy

00:34:19.630 --> 00:34:20.570
To heal your wounds.

00:34:23.630 --> 00:34:25.650
Keep this money and protective talismans

00:34:26.470 --> 00:34:27.530
To safeguard yourself.

00:34:28.400 --> 00:34:29.130
Lifei,

00:34:30.110 --> 00:34:32.570
You're going to see His Highness, right?

00:34:34.670 --> 00:34:35.900
Take good care of yourself

00:34:36.360 --> 00:34:37.050
And your child.

00:34:42.440 --> 00:34:43.300
What are your odds?

00:34:48.070 --> 00:34:49.900
I'm Miaoqing. Greetings, Your Highness.

00:34:56.360 --> 00:34:57.530
Ji Tongzhou is using Gelin as bait,

00:34:57.840 --> 00:34:58.740
All to lure you here.

00:34:58.880 --> 00:34:59.700
If you go over there

00:34:59.800 --> 00:35:00.650
And he sees through your disguise...

00:35:02.320 --> 00:35:03.050
It won't happen.

00:35:03.880 --> 00:35:05.820
I've never failed at tricking anyone.

00:35:06.280 --> 00:35:06.780
No way.

00:35:07.510 --> 00:35:08.450
Ji Tongzhou is far too shrewd to be fooled.

00:35:10.590 --> 00:35:12.130
I know this is pulling chestnuts out of the fire,

00:35:12.670 --> 00:35:14.900
Yet we have no other options right now.

00:35:15.720 --> 00:35:16.490
Don't worry.

00:35:17.030 --> 00:35:18.740
I'll sneak in to find out where Gelin is.

00:35:18.920 --> 00:35:20.090
I'll avoid him at all costs if I can.

00:35:20.470 --> 00:35:21.090
Nothing will go wrong.

00:35:21.590 --> 00:35:22.340
I'm coming with you.

00:35:23.070 --> 00:35:23.530
You...

00:35:23.990 --> 00:35:24.610
You said

00:35:25.360 --> 00:35:25.970
Nothing would go wrong.

00:35:28.630 --> 00:35:30.260
It's settled then.

00:35:40.110 --> 00:35:42.010
Miaoqing, you're back!

00:35:43.320 --> 00:35:43.970
Mr. Zhao.

00:35:44.630 --> 00:35:45.860
It's been ages. Where have you been?

00:35:46.630 --> 00:35:47.380
While you were gone,

00:35:47.400 --> 00:35:48.780
His Highness was in a bad mood every day.

00:35:49.280 --> 00:35:50.490
We all hoped you'd return soon.

00:35:51.240 --> 00:35:52.740
I just wandered around.

00:35:53.070 --> 00:35:54.340
I've missed His Highness deeply, too.

00:35:55.800 --> 00:35:57.420
I heard Miss Baili visited

00:35:57.440 --> 00:35:58.860
His Highness the other day,

00:35:59.190 --> 00:36:01.050
And they seemed to argue.

00:36:01.440 --> 00:36:02.450
Did His Highness get hurt?

00:36:02.920 --> 00:36:04.090
She's no match for him.

00:36:04.760 --> 00:36:05.820
He locked her up long ago.

00:36:05.990 --> 00:36:06.700
Where is she being locked?

00:36:07.190 --> 00:36:07.700
She is...

00:36:12.630 --> 00:36:13.260
Miaoqing,

00:36:14.440 --> 00:36:15.700
Why bother yourself with this?

00:36:19.550 --> 00:36:19.940
Who's there?

00:36:21.720 --> 00:36:22.820
This Truth-Revealing Talisman

00:36:23.320 --> 00:36:25.450
Will make us safe and sound.

00:36:48.240 --> 00:36:48.780
Gelin!

00:36:50.670 --> 00:36:51.340
Miaoqing.

00:36:52.110 --> 00:36:52.970
Stand back.

00:37:00.590 --> 00:37:01.380
Lifei,

00:37:02.670 --> 00:37:03.420
You've come back.

00:37:12.960 --> 00:37:13.530
Yes.

00:37:14.670 --> 00:37:15.740
She's finally returned.

00:37:17.590 --> 00:37:18.700
Welcome home.

00:37:21.880 --> 00:37:22.740
Ji Tongzhou,

00:37:23.720 --> 00:37:24.570
You beast!

00:37:39.960 --> 00:37:41.010
It's been a decade.

00:37:42.030 --> 00:37:43.420
I've waited for this moment.

00:37:44.840 --> 00:37:46.050
Let's hold our wedding ceremony anew.

00:37:46.880 --> 00:37:47.530
This time,

00:37:47.800 --> 00:37:48.740
No one will ever tear you

00:37:48.760 --> 00:37:49.900
Away from me.

00:37:51.030 --> 00:37:52.420
We can stay together forever.

00:37:53.400 --> 00:37:54.010
That can't be.

00:37:54.760 --> 00:37:56.170
Xiuyuan and I are married.

00:37:57.840 --> 00:37:58.610
What did you say?

00:37:59.800 --> 00:38:01.970
She said we're married. Can't you understand?

00:38:04.440 --> 00:38:04.940
Lifei.

00:38:09.470 --> 00:38:10.650
Lei Xiuyuan!

00:38:14.070 --> 00:38:15.170
Ji Tongzhou!

00:38:19.840 --> 00:38:20.340
Watch out!

00:38:22.070 --> 00:38:22.490
Run!

00:38:28.960 --> 00:38:30.130
Why not unleash your Yecha power?

00:38:30.840 --> 00:38:31.780
You're the Demon Lord.

00:38:32.960 --> 00:38:34.490
Don't think the world will accept you

00:38:35.110 --> 00:38:36.300
Just because you ended the Sea Calamity.

00:38:36.920 --> 00:38:38.010
The Sea Calamity arose

00:38:38.320 --> 00:38:39.380
Precisely because of you.

00:38:40.400 --> 00:38:41.610
You're wrong.

00:38:42.960 --> 00:38:44.300
It was born from your own greed.

00:38:44.920 --> 00:38:46.380
The Divine Tree never fell in love with your ancestor.

00:38:47.320 --> 00:38:48.450
He coveted the Divine Tree's power,

00:38:48.470 --> 00:38:49.340
Hoping to seize it for himself.

00:38:50.470 --> 00:38:51.530
[Ancestor of the Ji clan] When he failed,

00:38:51.990 --> 00:38:52.970
He colluded with the immortal sects

00:38:53.400 --> 00:38:54.650
To ambush her in the East Sea,

00:38:54.840 --> 00:38:55.570
Costing her life.

00:38:56.360 --> 00:38:57.300
The ancient gods were furious

00:38:57.840 --> 00:38:59.940
And unleashed the Sea Calamity to punish you all.

00:39:51.630 --> 00:39:52.420
You're lying!

00:39:53.440 --> 00:39:54.780
Had your ancestor not absorbed

00:39:55.630 --> 00:39:56.170
The Divine Tree's power,

00:39:56.190 --> 00:39:57.700
How could he have forged the Xuanhua Karmic Fire?

00:39:58.760 --> 00:40:01.420
Tongzhou, you know better than anyone

00:40:01.670 --> 00:40:03.170
What is required to master the karmic fire.

00:40:07.070 --> 00:40:08.170
The Sea Calamity is long gone.

00:40:09.470 --> 00:40:10.970
It's time to let go of your obsession.

00:40:17.150 --> 00:40:18.300
You have attained an immortal physique,

00:40:19.150 --> 00:40:20.450
And we stand no match for you.

00:40:21.320 --> 00:40:22.740
Why can't you let this go?

00:40:25.360 --> 00:40:26.220
Let go?

00:40:27.720 --> 00:40:29.010
How could I ever let go?

00:40:29.800 --> 00:40:31.340
If you had not stubbornly gone your own way

00:40:31.990 --> 00:40:33.130
And left me all alone,

00:40:34.110 --> 00:40:35.650
The Sea Calamity would never have happened.

00:40:36.030 --> 00:40:38.380
Ye Ye and Changyue would still be alive.

00:40:39.110 --> 00:40:40.260
It is all your fault.

00:40:40.630 --> 00:40:42.380
Because you chose Yecha.

00:40:43.030 --> 00:40:43.820
Ji Tongzhou,

00:40:44.840 --> 00:40:45.650
Enough of your madness.

00:40:46.840 --> 00:40:47.970
All the slaughter is of your own making,

00:40:48.550 --> 00:40:49.900
But you shift the blame to others.

00:40:50.630 --> 00:40:52.220
How can you face Ye Ye and the rest?

00:40:53.880 --> 00:40:54.610
Mad?

00:40:58.720 --> 00:41:01.940
I only regret I didn't lose my mind sooner.

00:41:08.320 --> 00:41:09.860
Your Highness, stop,

00:41:10.070 --> 00:41:11.300
Or you will live to regret it.

00:41:11.470 --> 00:41:12.860
Even you betrayed me, too!

00:41:13.470 --> 00:41:13.970
Get lost!

00:41:30.240 --> 00:41:30.820
Xiuyuan!

00:41:44.030 --> 00:41:45.530
Uncle, save me!

00:41:46.840 --> 00:41:47.260
Release them,

00:41:47.920 --> 00:41:48.740
Or I'll kill him.

00:41:51.150 --> 00:41:51.610
Uncle,

00:41:52.550 --> 00:41:53.820
Lifei once saved my life

00:41:54.280 --> 00:41:55.050
And helped the Yue State.

00:41:55.800 --> 00:41:56.490
Spare them.

00:41:57.190 --> 00:41:58.170
Let there be no more killing.

00:41:58.720 --> 00:41:59.740
Let them leave.

00:41:59.880 --> 00:42:00.490
Silence!

00:42:01.440 --> 00:42:02.380
With such cowardice,

00:42:02.960 --> 00:42:04.570
How will you guard the Yue State's realm?

00:42:21.240 --> 00:42:21.820
Xiuyuan!

00:42:42.050 --> 00:42:42.360
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:42:42.360 --> 00:42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:42:55.800 --> 00:42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

00:42:59.800 --> 00:43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

00:43:02.560 --> 00:43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

00:43:05.800 --> 00:43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

00:43:09.200 --> 00:43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

00:43:13.360 --> 00:43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

00:43:16.720 --> 00:43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

00:43:23.080 --> 00:43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

00:43:27.480 --> 00:43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

00:43:30.360 --> 00:43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

00:43:32.400 --> 00:43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:43:36.880 --> 00:43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:43:41.080 --> 00:43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

00:43:44.160 --> 00:43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

00:43:50.480 --> 00:43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

00:44:07.440 --> 00:44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

00:44:11.400 --> 00:44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

00:44:14.280 --> 00:44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

00:44:17.680 --> 00:44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

00:44:21.160 --> 00:44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

00:44:25.160 --> 00:44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

00:44:28.600 --> 00:44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

00:44:35.000 --> 00:44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

00:44:39.200 --> 00:44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

00:44:42.160 --> 00:44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

00:44:44.160 --> 00:44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

00:44:48.600 --> 00:44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

00:44:52.720 --> 00:44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

00:44:55.960 --> 00:45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

00:45:02.720 --> 00:45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

00:45:06.920 --> 00:45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

00:45:09.800 --> 00:45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

00:45:11.880 --> 00:45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

00:45:16.360 --> 00:45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

00:45:20.440 --> 00:45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

00:45:23.600 --> 00:45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

00:45:30.000 --> 00:45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

